-- EU's Rehn: EU members to respect direct bank recaps
-- 
-- Mon Oct 1, 2012 8:45am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/01/us-spain-economy-banks-idUSBRE8900LD20121001

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - EU Economic and Monetary Affairs Commissioner Olli Rehn said on Monday he expects euro zone members to respect their commitments regarding direct bank recapitalizations as agreed at a summit in June. 
 Rehn was speaking in Madrid after a meeting with Spanish Economy Minister Luis de Guindos. (Reporting By Sarah Morris; Writing by Tracy Rucinski; Editing by Nigel Davies)